title: Great Lives From History: Incredibly Wealthy
description: The latest title in the award-winning "Great Lives from History" series, The Incredibly Wealthy covers 446 extremely rich individuals from ancient times through the present, worldwide. The vast majority of these individuals have not been covered in this series before, and certainly not from the perspective of how they generated and used their wealth. Many of these individuals are not covered in other biographical works of this magnitude. Plus, complimentary online access is provided through Salem History.
